韦尔》</em> 。这些节目以及 WBD 库中的许多其他节目<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/westworld-roku-tubi-warner-bros-discovery-ad-supported-channels-183905525.html">都可以</a>在 Roku、Tubi 和<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazons-freevee-is-adding-free-mgm-and-warner-bros-discovery-channels-144339161.html">Amazon Freevee</a>上的免费且有广告支持的频道上观看。</p><p>扎斯拉夫和他的团队采用了其他策略来提高 WBD 的底线。其中包括从 Max 中撤下许多<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbo-max-sesame-street-cost-cutting-183844638.html">节目</a>和电影以降低成本、在完成之前<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbo-max-halts-original-productions-across-large-parts-of-europe-130226456.html">取消</a><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbo-max-batman-animated-series-jj-abrams-bruce-timm-170056366.html">Max 独家项目</a>（据报道在某些情况下支持税收冲销）以及<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbo-max-layoffs-reality-kids-programming-184222650.html">解雇员工</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/hbo-shows-are-streaming-on-netflix-in-the-us-for-the-first-time-161235695.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hbo-shows-are-streaming-on-netflix-in-the-us-for-the-first-time-161235695.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6ea8aa50-82c4-4402-bf2f-406428b6bfdb</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2023 16:12:35 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688401160</ingested><modified> 2023-07-03T16:19:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content heig